heading: Law.
general-note: Here are entered general works on law or legal systems as well as collections of statutes not limited to a specific topic. Works on the science of law are entered. Jurisprudence.. Works on legislative enactments as a source of law, as distinct from constitutional law or from the law arising from judicial or administrative decisions are entered under. Statutes.. Works on the legislative process are entered under. Legislation.. Works on the interpretation of statutes and other laws are entered under. Law--Interpretation and construction..
